object.customQuery:
with current_batch as (
select
	bls.batch_id,
	bls.source_start_cutoff_datetime,
	bls.source_end_cutoff_datetime
from
	$$operational_schema.batch_load_summary bls
where
	bls.source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'
	and bls.batch_status = 'Inprogress'
	and bls.batch_id = (
	select
		MAX(batch_id)
	from
		$$operational_schema.batch_load_summary
	where
		source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'
		and batch_status = 'Inprogress' ))
select 
distinct 
src.source_name,
src.load_type,
src.id,
src.status,
src.action_type,
src."user",
src.job_id,
src.record_nup,
src.message,
src.created_time,
src.agency_nups,
adm_transfer_log_guidewire_row_id,
adm_transfer_log_guidewire_row_md5checksum,
tgt.id as tgt_id,
tgt.created_time as tgt_created_time,
adm_transfer_log_guidewire_row_effective_end_datetime,
current_batch.batch_id
FROM $$raw_schema.adm_transfer_log_guidewire src
left join $$staging_schema.adm_transfer_log_guidewire tgt
on src.id = tgt.id
and adm_transfer_log_guidewire_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
left join current_batch on true
